<h2>Set Operations</h2>
<p>The four important set operations that are widely used are:</p>
<ul>
<li style=3D"font-weight: 400;" aria-level=3D"1"><a href=3D"https://byjus.c=
om/maths/union-of-sets/"><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Union of sets</s=
pan></a></li>
<li style=3D"font-weight: 400;" aria-level=3D"1"><a href=3D"https://byjus.c=
om/maths/union-and-intersection-of-sets-cardinal-number-practical-problems/=
